{"tid":2505454,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登大量pr，玩膠佬真係搞唔撚掂","createTime":"2021-04-26T15:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T21:16:36.000Z","uid":310242,"like":56,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"81e8b54e132b10c66593836f437569c92155c53e","tid":2505454,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"個排屌試當真，然後到四台<br />\n近排就追擊viutv，193<br />\n<br />\n你老味波台狗就日屌夜屌cctoy，<br />\n笑柒2019場運動，啊豬啊狗都留言「手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n將「手足」一個正面，支持同路人嘅字搞到變左帶有諷刺負面標籤<br />\n<br />\n坦白講，2019年連登討論區團結左好多香港人，但宜家咁撚樣日日消耗內聚力。你話上連登睇on9野係好笑都仲好，宜家上連登就係一班on9做緊令人煩厭嘅事<br />\n<br />\n連登討論區，根本無討論過，唔係我屌柒你，就係你屌柒我<br />\n當然你會話「新會然第一日上連登？」<br />\n但個情況就係愈黎愈嚴重，係咪無得救"},{"pid":"48d0605da8910270a37dcb11220e83a7344f9d0f","tid":2505454,"uid":310242,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T15:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZGWCe3ohFnr7KaZK35psV2N4aZZQnfoz5jjfrAppvv88?filename=b3G6c5T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb3G6c5T.png&h=f41d6e51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8b0b178eb35b0d7744763b687ea4eb61dc6ca96","tid":2505454,"uid":310242,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T15:15:49.000Z","msg":"負評嘅講下你諗法啦，話明討論區又唔撚討論，係咪要屌柒全世界先叫合連登文化"},{"pid":"03a502c5609cd0abb1643bf63bfeb676b1f19e7b","tid":2505454,"uid":7359,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T15:46:44.000Z","msg":"呢個正經po 就冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df00a21b6b3f403a9bfc604957ed0834ccc3674b","tid":2505454,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03a502c5609cd0abb1643bf63bfeb676b1f19e7b","tid":2505454,"uid":7359,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T15:46:44.000Z","msg":"呢個正經po 就冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:14:12.000Z"